243
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:41,880
Xinxin.

244
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,040
Let me see her.

245
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,520
Ming.

246
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,420
Later, tell Wan Xinxin

247
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:07,920
