283
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:37,540
He's instructed that we drop the matter.

284
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,440
You received the compensation?

285
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,080
Yes.

286
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:43,200
Your boyfriend delivered it personally this morning.

287
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,130
Didn't you know?

288
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,200
My boyfriend?

289
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:47,980
Anyway,

290
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,880
I have another meeting to attend. Let's talk later.

291
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:54,880
I hope we can work together next time, okay?

292
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,440
Mr. Shi.

293
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:06,920
Mr. Shi.

294
00:17:08,359 --> 00:17:09,760
UBay Group just called.

295
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:13,119
They've officially withdrawn their lawsuit against us.

296
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:15,200
Also,

297
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:17,960
two minutes ago our company account received money from

298
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,400
a private account under the name Xu Ke,

299
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:21,260
a transfer of 1.5 million in cash.

300
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:31,840
Wan Xinxin.

301
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,300
Wan Xinxin.

302
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:46,260
Why didn't you tell me when something happened?

303
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:49,720
No. Telling anyone about this is useless.

304
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,250
I have to solve this myself.

305
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:52,680
How will you solve it?

306
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,680
By running away with your child?

307
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,060
Is that your solution?

308
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:59,820
Where can you possibly run to?

309
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:02,120
No, if I stay here...

310
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:04,600
I can't let Mr. Shi's company go bankrupt.

311
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:05,560
But I also can't let Qin Gang

312
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:07,020
take my child away from me.

313
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:10,960
Do you think that by doing this

314
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,620
Shi Lu will be grateful to you?

315
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:13,680
If you do this,

316
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:15,520
you'll have a clear conscience?

317
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,900
You're forcing others to accept your kindness.

318
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:21,360
After you run away with the child,

319
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:23,420
the father will be gone from his life.

320
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,240
I'll just tell him

321
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,600
his father died when he was born.

322
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:27,060
That's called deception.

323
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:30,240
When the child grows up, he has the right to know his origins.

324
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,570
You can lie to yourself,

325
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:33,810
but you can't lie to him.

326
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,400
Because you're his mother.

327
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,000
You don't-

328
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:50,880
Hello?

329
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:54,760
She's right here with me.

330
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:56,140
Tell her yourself.

331
00:18:57,320 --> 00:18:57,680
Xu Ke.

332
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,560
Xinxin, um...

333
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:09,600
I'm sorry.

334
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,680
I didn't discuss it with you,

335
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:13,120
but I've sold the house.

336
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:13,840
What?

337
00:19:15,120 --> 00:19:17,440
But don't worry.

338
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:19,600
I've already spoken with the buyer.

339
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:22,280
You can stay for two more days,

340
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:24,290
we'll figure things out later.

341
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:25,960
However, after that,

342
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,960
you and your son will have to make do.

343
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:29,640
You can stay at my

344
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:31,490
small rented apartment, okay?

345
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:35,040
Alright, don't be so dramatic.

346
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:37,680
I need to pack for a business trip.

347
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:39,240
Wait until I get back.

348
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:42,760
Take good care of yourself and your son.

349
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,040
I got it.

350
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:52,400
No, but do you think this guy will be okay?

351
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:54,800
He sold his house to pay back Shi Lu's money.

352
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:57,200
So he's your bestie.

353
00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:58,800
You two think exactly alike.

354
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:01,560
Oh no, how did I end up dragging him into this too?

355
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,400
Anyway,

356
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:06,880
what Xu Ke did was really decent.

357
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:10,930
Even if you're running away, you should thank him in person.

358
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:19,120
Hello, Mr. Shi.

359
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:22,880
Wan Xinxin, where is Xu Ke now?

360
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:24,520
You must help me find him.

361
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:26,120
I have something to tell him.

362
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:30,440
Is there an apartment building across from your place?

363
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,500
He should be there.

364
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:34,320
What? He lives across from us?

365
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:10,880
Are you crazy, Xu Huahua?

366
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,410
Why did you sell your house?

367
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:16,000
Um, Xinxin, I'm sorry.

368
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,460
What are you sorry for?

369
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:19,360
This has nothing to do with you.

370
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:23,760
No, I was the one who recommended this job to you.

371
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:25,320
If something goes wrong, I must take responsibility.

372
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:28,050
This has absolutely nothing to do with you, okay?

373
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,540
You can't say that.

374
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:30,560
You're my friend.

375
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:32,800
That person over there is my future lover.

376
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:34,240
And there's my godson too.

377
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:37,900
Both emotionally and rationally, I have responsibility in this.

378
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:41,600
Alright.

379
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,680
No more drama.

380
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:47,220
So here's the plan.

381
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:48,840
I just got a big job.

382
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:50,360
When I come back with the money,

383
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:52,720
we'll rent a bigger place. How's that?

384
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:56,080
Ming,

385
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,240
about the moving stuff,

386
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,800
please take care of it, okay?

387
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:00,860
Sure, don't worry.

388
00:22:14,040 --> 00:22:15,920
My keys

389
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:19,800
are under the doormat at my place.

390
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,140
Nobody knows about it.

391
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:34,490
Is that okay?

392
00:23:34,840 --> 00:23:35,440
Slow down.

393
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,080
Okay.

394
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:43,480
No, why don't you meet her later?

395
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:44,360
I won't.

396
00:23:45,080 --> 00:23:47,340
Why not? Just meet her once before you go.

397
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:49,820
Forget it. Better not to meet.

398
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:51,600
No, wait!

399
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:53,530
I already told her you're here.

400
00:23:54,080 --> 00:23:55,200
No, you...

401
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,880
Why do you always make things difficult for me?

402
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:58,080
She's my boss.

403
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,000
Look,

404
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,240
tell her later

405
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,120
that what I'm doing

406
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:02,850
isn't to win her over, you know?

407
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,920
No, how am I supposed to tell her?

408
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:07,800
Just meet her once before you go.

409
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:10,770
Look, you talk to her yourself.

410
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:25,680
You deliberately came to see me off.

411
00:24:27,360 --> 00:24:28,680
Why did you do that?

412
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:33,180
Don't worry. It's not for you anyway.

413
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,920
I just want you to know

414
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:37,080
not all men are just smooth talkers.

415
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:40,440
You don't need to prove anything to me.

416
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:42,100
I don't need your help either.

417
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:48,130
Can you not be so intense when you talk?

418
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:50,250
Can you be a little gentler?

419
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:52,640
What does it matter to you whether I'm gentle or not?

420
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:53,760
Of course it matters.

421
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:55,420
I like you, so it matters to me.

422
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,280
I will never like you.

423
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,000
Don't think that by doing this,

424
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:00,930
I'll be touched.

425
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:03,120
Let me tell you, it's impossible.

426
00:25:04,880 --> 00:25:06,720
I'm not trying to touch you either.

427
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:09,200
Me liking you is my own issue.

428
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,720
It has nothing to do with you.

429
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:13,050
And I'm not asking for anything in return.

430
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:17,240
Investing in something with no return?

431
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:19,400
Are you an idiot?

432
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:23,920
Love isn't an investment. Why be so smart about it?

433
00:25:27,360 --> 00:25:28,490
Cat got your tongue?

434
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,600
Don't be so uptight. Relax.

435
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:35,210
I'll pay you back within three months.

436
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:37,980
I'll also pay you the appropriate interest.

437
00:25:38,520 --> 00:25:39,400
That won't do.

438
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:41,320
Then I'd be working for nothing.

439
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,000
What else do you want?

440
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:47,240
Shares.

441
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:49,800
What?

442
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:53,200
I've wanted to invest for a long time.

443
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:56,480
But before, your company was so big.

444
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:58,800
So now when your company is at its most difficult time,

445
00:25:58,800 --> 00:26:00,160
I'm taking advantage of the situation.

446
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:01,840
What's that professional term called?

447
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:02,770
Bottom fishing.

448
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:06,320
Then I'll become a shareholder in your company.

449
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:08,480
When your company develops well,

450
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:10,680
I'll rise to prosperity with it, right?

451
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,760
After that, I won't have to worry about my livelihood

452
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,760
and run around everywhere anymore.

453
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:19,000
Director Shi, do you agree with what I'm saying?

454
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:26,480
Fine. I'll give you a proportional share.

455
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:28,040
That's a must.

456
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,280
Well, I

457
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:33,280
will be a shareholder in your company from now on.

458
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:34,680
You're all my employees.

459
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:36,410
You all need to work hard for me.

460
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,920
Work harder and take good care of my little investment.

461
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:41,840
I'm counting on you all for the rest of my life.

462
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,020
Give me a break.

463
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,320
Hey, Ming.

464
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:48,520
So...

465
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:52,000
While I'm gone, I'm leaving these two in your care.

466
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:54,130
Take it easy.

467
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:55,680
He's gone.

468
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:56,560
Take care.

469
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:58,170
Just go already.

470
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,330
Wait for me to come back.

471
00:27:14,840 --> 00:27:15,570
Go after him.

472
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,520
Xu Ke.

473
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:19,970
I'll see you off.

474
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,380
Great. That's wonderful.

475
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:34,760
If I don't personally see you off far away,

476
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:35,890
I won't feel at ease.

477
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:38,680
That's fine, that's fine. Whatever works.

478
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:43,960
Director Shi, slow down.

479
00:27:44,600 --> 00:27:45,240
Goodbye.

480
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:52,130
Let's go.

481
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:55,940
This outcome is a bit unexpected.

482
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,040
Kaiyang.

483
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:18,490
Yesterday I heard you on the phone with Mr. Zheng.

484
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:19,920
He said their factory

485
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:21,240
wanted you to come by,

486
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:23,240
and they've kept a position for you.

487
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:26,560
It's just a small rundown machinery factory without even a Party committee.

488
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:27,680
What's the point?

489
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:29,040
Well...

490
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:31,640
I heard Liu's timber factory

491
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:34,880
is importing equipment to process wooden doors.

492
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,610
Why don't you go work with them?

493
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:38,050
I'm not a carpenter.

494
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:39,040
What would I do there?

495
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:40,680
Run errands? Sell doors?

496
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:44,680
What about Mr. Zhang's place?

497
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:47,040
Enough, Xu Chunli.

498
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:48,280
Do you feel

499
00:28:48,280 --> 00:28:49,540
I'm in your way at home?

500
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:52,400
Listen to yourself.

501
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:55,320
I'd love for you to stay home with me all day.

502
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:58,320
But you can't just stay at home forever.

503
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:00,720
Why don't you find something to do first,

504
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:03,380
and if it doesn't work out, you can change later?

505
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:09,440
How's the relationship between Qin Gang

506
00:29:09,560 --> 00:29:10,620
and Wan Xinxin now?

507
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,880
What do you expect?

508
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:15,560
Qin Gang keeps pestering Xinxin now,

509
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:16,980
wanting to see his son.

510
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,740
Serves him right. Now he cares about his son?

511
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:22,400
Where was he before? I won't let him see the boy.

512
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:24,080
That's not right, Xu Chunli.

513
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,160
We can't do that.

514
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,960
Even though they're divorced,

515
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,840
Qin Gang is still the child's father.

516
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:31,600
Not letting a father see his child

517
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:33,460
makes no sense. It's our mistake.

518
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,530
Why are you taking his side?

519
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:39,520
Have you forgotten how Qin Gang treated Xinxin before?

520
00:29:39,520 --> 00:29:42,000
You don't understand. Since ancient times...

521
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,040
Get out of the way!

522
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:47,400
Since ancient times, people always advise reconciliation, not separation, right?

523
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:49,660
As her sister, you should be helping her.

524
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:51,640
What do you mean?

525
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:54,120
What I mean is that as her sister,

526
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:56,680
when Xinxin is in trouble,

527
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:57,610
you as her sister

528
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:59,560
should help her as much as you can.

529
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:02,720
For example, help her look after her child

530
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:03,980
to lighten her burden.

531
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:05,460
Shouldn't you do that?

532
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:06,840
You're right.

533
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,640
About that 100,000 yuan,

534
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:10,500
we really did wrong by Xinxin.

535
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,290
I'll go check on her in a bit.

536
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,440
Yes, exactly.

537
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:14,560
Hey,

538
00:30:15,040 --> 00:30:16,100
do you understand?

539
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:18,040
Got it. I'll check on her later.

540
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,440
No, can you smile a bit?

541
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,680
Don't be so cold, okay?

542
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,900
It's just that you seem

543
00:30:43,080 --> 00:30:45,540
like you're carrying some deep heartbreak.

544
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:47,920
You can tell me about it.

545
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:50,020
I can help you work through it.

546
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:58,890
Why are we stopping?

547
00:30:59,760 --> 00:31:01,760
We haven't reached the airport yet.

548
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:05,180
What's wrong with you?

549
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:09,920
Even if you're a shareholder,

550
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:12,180
I'm not obligated to fake a smile for you.

551
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:15,280
I was just kidding.

552
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:18,420
Why are you upset? Look, you're angry again.

553
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:20,160
What I mean is,

554
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,880
someone like you must have either

555
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:23,720
lost your parents as a child,

556
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:24,600
or

557
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:26,400
met some jerk when you first fell in love,

558
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:29,800
completely destroying your beautiful outlook on the world.

559
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:36,610
You want to hear a story, right?

560
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:40,560
Well, I have an even more touching story.

561
